episodes.title: [From 0:20:16] FULL SHOW | Cult Survivor Escape Story, Best Coffee in Perth, WA Footy Star in Town Ryan Daniels Has the Details.
episodes.description: Big show today, the latest edition of Ask Me Anything, we spoke to a cult survivor who was born into a cult but escaped, we heard his story. Ryan Daniels has some details about a WA footy star who is in Perth. By the end of this week we will know where the best coffee in Perth is hiding.
